data.description: OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY 1/7/2024 FROM 2-4PM!!!  Move in Ready!! Go and Show!! 2 bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths townhome. Nice size kitchen, with living room, eat in area, and 1/2 bath located on the 1st floor. All new flooring on the 1st level, new paint throughout the townhome. Patio in the back to enjoy the outdoors. Two spacious bedrooms, primary bedroom has vaulted ceilings, shutter blinds, two closets, and a spacious bathroom. Laundry room is located upstairs. Additional bedroom also have vaulted ceilings, a full bathroom and a walk in closet. Convenient location, close to shops, restaurants, PTI airport, and highways.
